modName: CBBE Master Mage Robe Replacer with CBBE Nocturnal Robe
summary: BigBoobs! Only Female-This is a Replacer for the original Master Mage Robe with the CBBE Nocturnal robe. Enjoy.
descriptionHtml:
Only Female-Requires the CBBE installed in order to work properly.
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

This is a Replacer for the original Master Mage Robe with the CBBE Nocturnal robe. Enjoy.

All the credits for Caliente since this is his mod and his editions, I just made the replacement.

[b][color=#FF0000]Original CBBE: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666
Nocturnal Robe CBBE (replaces fine clothes) : http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2676[/color]
[/b]
If you get any bugs just let me know and Sorry for shadows in the screens that may get skin looking weird. I have set them to lowest to run game smoothly. 

Thanks to Caliente.
